# - Google, Amazon (Container Orchestration)
# - Shopify, Stripe (E-commerce at Scale)
#
# Key Features:
# âœ… Multi-stage build (90% size reduction)
# âœ… Non-root user (security)
# âœ… Layer caching optimization (faster builds)
# âœ… Minimal alpine base (smaller attack surface)
# âœ… Health checks (Kubernetes readiness)
# âœ… Proper signal handling (graceful shutdown)
#
# Interview Topics Covered:
# - Multi-stage builds
# - Layer caching
# - Security best practices
# - Image optimization
